@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam roundCorner 15
skinparam shadowing true
[*] --> Cancelled
Cancelled --> Archived : review
Archived --> Reviewed : confirm
Reviewed --> Processing : update
Reviewed : entry / log publisher
Processing --> Approved : submit
Processing : entry / log publisher
Processing --> Archived : revert
Approved --> [*]
@enduml